e-mail: promed@promedmail.org
[This is an unconfirmed media report that lacks specific information about
the cause(s) of the outbreaks. I edited out a sentence that included an
indication in that the increased caseload was associated with the approach
of the summer season. Perhaps dairy products are not properly refrigerated,
thereby exacerbating the problem. We would appreciate further information
about the etiology. - Mod. ES
